  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MTA47">
<l>vāri curukki matakkaḷi ṟaintiṉaiyuñ</l>
<l>cēri tiriyāmaṟ cenniṟīi – kūriya</l>
<l>meyññāṉat tāluṇarvār kāṇparē mēlorunāṭ</l>
<l>kainnākaṅ kāttāṉ kaḻal</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who understand with sharp true knowledge, keeping straight</l>
<l>all the five rutting elephants (the senses) so as not to roam the streets,</l>
<l>by lessening the [musth] water, they will see the anklet[ed] feet of the one</l> 
<l>who protected the elephant on a former day.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
